ion. Lialda (mesalamine (5-aminosalicylic acid))." Shire US Inc, Florence, KY.[4] Novis BH, Korzets Z, Chen P, Bernheim J "Nephrotic syndrome after treatment with 5-aminosalicylic acid." Br Med J (Clin Res Ed) 296 (1988): 1442', 1767363021);
